data.description: Incredible contemporary and open floorplan with a fantastic view of the Omaha skyline. Enjoy a spacious kitchen featuring Corian countertops and vaulted ceilings. Massive walk-out family room and flex room on the lower level with a 3 car tandem garage. Plenty of upgrades to consider from low maintenance composite decking to solar panels on the roof that will cut your utility bills down drastically. Come view this incredible home in Miami Heights. A taste of west Omaha suburban living while being mere minutes from Downtown.
